snippet.title: Best VGM 881 - Double Dragon - Arrival of the Black Warriors (Stage 1)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES
Double Dragon (1988)
Arrival of the Black Warriors (Stage 1)
Kazunaka Yamane
